## Your API Keys (YOU NEED TO FILL THESE IN)

### 1. Get Alchemy API Key

1. Go to: https://www.alchemy.com/
2. Sign up for a free account
3. Click "Create App"
4. Select:
   - Chain: **Ethereum**
   - Network: **Sepolia**
   - Name: "Messaging App Test"
5. Copy your API key
6. Paste it below:

```env
VITE_ALCHEMY_KEY="paste_your_alchemy_key_here"
```

### 2. Get WalletConnect Project ID

1. Go to: https://cloud.walletconnect.com/
2. Sign up for a free account
3. Click "Create New Project"
4. Name it "Messaging App Test"
5. Copy your Project ID
6. Paste it below:

```env
VITE_WALLET_CONNECT_PROJECT_ID="paste_your_walletconnect_id_here"
```

---

## Optional: IPFS Storage (Pinata)

If you want to use real IPFS storage instead of localStorage:

1. Go to: https://pinata.cloud/
2. Sign up for a free account
3. Go to API Keys section
4. Create a new API key with these permissions:
   - pinFileToIPFS
   - pinJSONToIPFS
5. Copy your keys:

```env
VITE_PINATA_API_KEY="your_pinata_api_key"
VITE_PINATA_SECRET_KEY="your_pinata_secret_key"
VITE_PINATA_JWT="your_pinata_jwt"
```

---

